726280f-a.title: Queens: Brookville Boulevard - 136th Avenue
726280f-a.text:
Brookville Boulevard, west side, between 136th and 137th
Avenues, showing the old Public School No. 38. It became an
annex to P. S. 38 when a new building was erected for the
school at 241st Street and 15th Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  March 9, 1927
